Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer, for sale or lease, 82 Drake Boulevard, Altona. 

82 Drake Boulevard, Altona is located in Hobson Bay’s most sought after industrial estate, Access Altona.  
This position offers occupiers superior connectivity throughout Melbourne with direct access to the West Gate Freeway and Princes Freeway. The rare pocket of Industrial 1 zoning also offers owners and occupiers the most flexible range of uses and least restrictions.   

This inner west position offers excellent amenities including the popular estate café and its proximity to Williamstown, Altona Train Station and main retail strip, Pier Street.

Key building features; 
+	10m* spring height 
+	High quality fitted corporate offices, showroom and amenities 
+	Ideal display yard/hardstand area
+	Prominent corner location 
+	Immediate freeway accessibility 
+	Ideally located amongst high profile neighbours such as DB Schenker, Form 700, Godfreys and more
+	Within the sought-after Access Altona Estate, considered the most premium estate in the Western industrial market
+	Ability to accommodate a wide range of occupiers 
+	Drive through capability 
+	Multiple RSD’s with extra height and width 
+	Large crossovers 
+	Site area: 3,858sqm*
+	Approximate building area including mezzanine of 2,100sqm* 
+      Solar system installed, miniman utility costs
+      Security features throughout including shutters, cameras and monitored alarm
+      Fully fitted offices and furniture available
+      Pallet racking available

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the CBRE team.

*approximate

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE & Colliers International are excited to present Warehouse B, 18-34 Aylesbury Drive, Altona, for lease.

Located within the premier Access Altona Estate, this property provides excellent connections to Melbourne’s major road network including the West Gate Freeway, Princes Freeway and Western Ring Road. Located approximately 9km west of the Port of Melbourne, 13km west of Melbourne's CBD and 20km south of the Melbourne Airport.

Warehouse B, 18-34 Aylesbury Drive offers the following key features:

+   Total site area: 14,730sqm*
+   Total building Area: 9,077sqm*
+   10m high clearance warehouse 8,768sqm*
+   Corporate office and staff amenities: 309sqm*
+   36m super awning for all weather loading
+   Four (4) on-grade roller doors
+   Two (2) recessed docks
+   ESFR sprinkler system with shared tank/pumps for reduced outgoings
+   Full B-Double compliant hardstand
+   Ample on-site car parking (55 bays)
+   Multiple crossovers
+   Separate car and truck entry/exit
+   Compliant for Tyre storage

For further information or to arrange an on-site inspection, please contact the exclusively appointed CBRE or Colliers International agents.
